Welcome to the Netlabs EPM Distribution Package by
OS/2 Netlabs (http://www.netlabs.org)

This package installs support files for the Enhanced Editor (EPM) including macro and REXX support, additional macros, extended syntax hilighting support, extended recompile support and many more.

